<DocsLayout>
  <h1>Mirrow CLI in a Nutshell</h1>
  <p>
    The Mirrow CLI takes a <code>.mirrow</code> file and compiles it into clean SVG.
    One command turns your DSL into a production ready asset.
  </p>

  <pre><code>npx mirrow -i icon.mirrow -o icon.svg</code></pre>

  <p>
    The CLI handles parsing, validation (numbers, tuples, CSS exceptions, hex
    colors), and codegen. Use it locally, in CI, or inside build scripts to
    generate icons, graphics, and animations on demand.
  </p>
</DocsLayout>
